Former Senator of Kaduna Central, Senator Shehu Sani has taken to his official Twitter handle to send a message to the former aide of Goodluck Jonathan, Reno Omokri after reports had it that the President, Muhammadu Buhari has jetted out of the country to the United Kingdom for medical attention.

This news was confirmed following multiple pictures of the president released by the presidency on Sunday 6th March 2022. Recall that Reno Omokri had posted on his official Facebook page recently that it was because of him that the president canceled his planned trip to the United Kingdom from his international duties in Kenya.

However, after several news outlets confirmed that the president has proceeded to London for medical attention, former Senator Shehu Sani decided to offer Reno Omokri and other protesters some advice. According to him, he said, “Baba has gone to London, people like @renoomokri and other protesters should concentrate on Ukraine please”.


